title: For Sale:  GLOCK 30 Gen4 45ACP NIB
postcontent: The Glock 30 Gen4 is ideal for home defense, concealed carry or as a duty weapon. It is a compact size, .45ACP, polymer frame handgun that uses a locked breach system referred to as "Safe Action". This is the combination of a trigger safety, firing pin safety and drop safety that render the loaded pistol incapable of firing, even when banged or bumped, unless someone actually squeezes the trigger. Three full capacity 10- round magazines are provided with Glock 30 Gen4 pistols. A set of white outline sights sit on top of the slide, are highly visible, easy to use and track reasonably well. The 3.78" hexagonal hammer forged barrel of the Glock 30 Gen4 increase muzzle velocity and provide greater accuracy than conventional rifled barrels. Overall, the Glock 30 Gen4 is a powerful, compact, accurate and versatile self-defense handgun that is built for a lifetime of reliable service.
